---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'; import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro'; import { games, guideTopics } from '../data/games';
const styles = [['Action','⚔','Fast reflexes, close combat, pure adrenaline.'],['Cards','♠','Deckbuilding and tactical card combat.'],['Tactics','♞','Grid-based strategy and careful planning.'],['Shooter','⌾','Guns, bullets, and screen-clearing chaos.'],['Co-op','♣','Team up with friends for chaotic co-op runs.']] as const;
const color = {Action:'var(--action)',Cards:'var(--cards)',Tactics:'var(--tactics)',Shooter:'var(--shooter)','Co-op':'var(--coop)'};
---
<BaseLayout title="Rogue On Switch — Find your next great run"><SiteHeader /><main class="shell"><section class="hero"><div><h1>Find your next<br />great run on<br /><em>Nintendo Switch.</em></h1><p>Rogue On Switch is an independent editorial directory<br />of roguelikes and roguelites playable on Nintendo Switch.<br />Curated lists, honest takes, and practical filters<br />to help you find games you’ll love.</p><a class="button" href="#browse"><svg class="button-arrow" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M0 6h7V2h4v4h5v4h-5v4H7v-4H0z" /></svg>Explore games</a></div><div class="hero-art" aria-label="Pixel-art dungeon explorer at a ruined gate"></div></section><section class="section"><p class="kicker">Browse by playstyle</p><div class="playstyles">{styles.map(([name,icon,copy]) => <a class="playstyle" data-icon={icon} href={`/genre/${name.toLowerCase()}/`} style={`--color:${color[name]}`}><b>{name}</b><span>{copy}</span></a>)}</div></section><section class="section"><p class="kicker">Editor's pick</p><div class="feature"><div class="feature-visual"><h2>Hades</h2></div><div class="feature-copy"><h2>Defy the god of the dead.</h2><p>As you hack and slash through the ever-shifting Underworld. Tight combat, meaningful choices, and unforgettable characters make every run feel epic.</p><span class="type" style="--type:var(--action)">Action</span></div><div class="feature-guidance"><div><h3>Best for</h3><p><span class="pixel-mark pixel-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M0 6h3v3h3v3h3V9h3V6h3V3h-3v3H9v3H6V6H3v3H0z" /></svg></span>Players who enjoy fast combat and fluid movement<br /><span class="pixel-mark pixel-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M0 6h3v3h3v3h3V9h3V6h3V3h-3v3H9v3H6V6H3v3H0z" /></svg></span>Those who love strong progression between runs<br /><span class="pixel-mark pixel-check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M0 6h3v3h3v3h3V9h3V6h3V3h-3v3H9v3H6V6H3v3H0z" /></svg></span>Anyone who wants a story that unfolds as they play</p></div><div><h3 class="skip">Skip if</h3><p><span class="pixel-mark pixel-cross" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M0 3h3v3h3V3h3V0h4v3h-3v3h3v4h-3v3h3v3H9v-3H6v-3H3v3H0v-3h3V6H0z" /></svg></span>You prefer turn-based or slow-paced combat<br /><span class="pixel-mark pixel-cross" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M0 3h3v3h3V3h3V0h4v3h-3v3h3v4h-3v3h3v3H9v-3H6v-3H3v3H0v-3h3V6H0z" /></svg></span>You want long, careful planning between runs<br /><span class="pixel-mark pixel-cross" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M0 3h3v3h3V3h3V0h4v3h-3v3h3v4h-3v3h3v3H9v-3H6v-3H3v3H0v-3h3V6H0z" /></svg></span>You’re not into frequent restarts on failure</p></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="browse"><div class="directory-head"><p class="kicker">Browse games</p><div class="filters"><button class="filter">All genres</button><button class="filter">Any run length</button><button class="filter">Any price</button><button class="filter">Co-op</button><button class="filter">Sort: Featured</button></div><a class="reset" href="#browse">Reset filters</a></div><table class="game-table"><thead><tr><th>Game</th><th>Run length</th><th>Price (USD)</th><th>Genre</th><th>Playstyle</th><th>Co-op</th></tr></thead><tbody>{games.slice(0,5).map(game => <tr><td><a href={`/games/${game.slug}/`}>{game.title}</a></td><td>{game.runLength}</td><td>{game.price}</td><td>{game.genre}, {game.classification}</td><td><span class="type" style={`--type:${color[game.playstyle]}`}>{game.playstyle}</span></td><td>{game.coOp}</td></tr>)}</tbody></table></section><section class="section"><div class="field-guide"><div><p class="kicker">The field guide</p><h2>Useful answers, not store copy.</h2><p>Deep dives, genre explainers, and practical guides to help you get the most out of roguelikes.</p></div>{guideTopics.slice(0,3).map(([,title,copy]) => <a href={`/best/${title.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g,'-').replace(/-$/,'')}/`}><h3>{title}</h3><p>{copy}</p></a>)}</div></section></main><footer class="footer"><a class="brand" href="/"><strong>ROGUE</strong><span>ON SWITCH</span></a><p>Rogue On Switch is an independent editorial directory and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any game developer, publisher, or platform holder.</p><span>About　 Contact　 Editorial Policy　 Privacy</span></footer></BaseLayout>
